Your dumplings allowed us to have a private rehearsal.

778
00:53:43,700 --> 00:53:47,180
 Yes! 

779
00:53:50,480 --> 00:53:52,120
Kang Hoon.

780
00:53:53,020 --> 00:53:56,200
I need to be careful since I'm on parole right now.

781
00:53:56,200 --> 00:53:59,980
I can't come out in the open for now.

782
00:53:59,980 --> 00:54:02,220
That's why I'd like you to help me.

783
00:54:02,220 --> 00:54:04,470
If you disappoint me like this,

784
00:54:04,470 --> 00:54:07,310
would I be angry or not?

785
00:54:07,950 --> 00:54:09,460
Huh?

786
00:54:10,440 --> 00:54:12,470
You bastard.

787
00:54:18,030 --> 00:54:22,020
I-I-I really did what you told me to.

788
00:54:22,020 --> 00:54:24,450
 You did, huh? But you warned them. Right? 

789
00:54:24,450 --> 00:54:30,860
No, I really removed all the screws in the stage equipment, as you told me.

790
00:54:30,860 --> 00:54:32,580
Did you tell them to cancel it?

791
00:54:32,580 --> 00:54:37,550
No, I said. They really canceled the rehearsal on their own.

792
00:54:41,870 --> 00:54:43,920
Didn't I tell you?

793
00:54:44,980 --> 00:54:47,850
That I have a sensitive back?

794
00:54:47,850 --> 00:54:54,390
I'll never forgive anyone for stabbing me in the back.

795
00:54:54,390 --> 00:54:56,150
Do Jin!

796
00:55:01,580 --> 00:55:04,700
Those bastards are rehearsing right now.

797
00:55:04,700 --> 00:55:07,800
I saw them sneaking into school at night, so I followed them.

798
00:55:07,800 --> 00:55:10,280
I think they got a key by bribing the security guard.

799
00:55:10,280 --> 00:55:14,110
What do you want to do? Should we attack them? Should we, Do Jin?

800
00:55:14,110 --> 00:55:17,930
I'm grateful that they fell into the trap on their own.

801
00:55:17,930 --> 00:55:19,770
I know.

802
00:55:26,260 --> 00:55:28,280
You have a poor taste for an heiress.

803
00:55:28,280 --> 00:55:31,650
What? It reminds me of Squid Game. I like it.

804
00:55:34,460 --> 00:55:39,150
 Squid Game? It hasn't been made in 1995. 

805
00:55:39,150 --> 00:55:41,460
Right. Do you want to stop by the restroom?

806
00:55:41,460 --> 00:55:45,420
I'll go before the movie starts. I'll go now.

807
00:55:46,590 --> 00:55:49,200
 Is it a '95 style joke? 

808
00:55:52,860 --> 00:55:54,510
   

809
00:55:58,040 --> 00:55:59,270
 First message. 

810
00:55:59,270 --> 00:56:02,350
 Hey, Ha Eun Gyeol. We'll rehearse at the gym right now. 

811
00:56:02,350 --> 00:56:06,060
 Come to the gym as soon as you check this message. 

812
00:56:09,920 --> 00:56:12,540
Hey, the movie's about to start! Where are you going?

813
00:56:12,540 --> 00:56:13,970
Hey, Ha Eun Gyeol!

814
00:56:13,970 --> 00:56:17,630
♪  I love you  ♪

815
00:56:17,630 --> 00:56:21,010
♪  You mean the world to me  ♪

816
00:56:21,010 --> 00:56:23,870
♪  I scream at the top of my lungs  ♪

817
00:56:23,870 --> 00:56:31,570
♪  But the sunset is firing up without an answer  ♪

818
00:56:41,610 --> 00:56:43,140
 No way. 

819
00:56:43,140 --> 00:56:45,320
 Yoon Dong Jin wasn't the helper? 

820
00:56:45,320 --> 00:56:49,660
 Or is it like, "Whatever has to happen, happens?" 

821
00:56:49,660 --> 00:56:50,930
 It doesn't matter. 

822
00:56:50,930 --> 00:56:54,000
 I'll stop this. I'll stop it, no matter what. 

823
00:57:07,070 --> 00:57:08,500
Long time no see, Kang Hyeon Yool.

824
00:57:08,500 --> 00:57:09,900
Hyeon Yool, your brothers are here!

825
00:57:09,900 --> 00:57:12,900
What's happening?

826
00:57:18,070 --> 00:57:22,460
Hey, hey, hey. Kang Hyeon Yool, do you know them by chance?

827
00:57:35,230 --> 00:57:37,590
Right, I have a present.

828
00:57:38,820 --> 00:57:40,390
My Hoon.

829
00:57:41,690 --> 00:57:44,140
Ding-dong.

830
00:57:46,090 --> 00:57:50,700
I heard he messed with your stage earlier today. Right?

831
00:57:50,700 --> 00:57:54,830
Why did you do something I didn't even tell you to?

832
00:58:01,580 --> 00:58:04,260
How does it feel to be stabbed in the back?

833
00:58:04,260 --> 00:58:08,250
- Do Jin. 
 - I'll tell you what happens...

834
00:58:08,250 --> 00:58:10,570
when you stab someone in the back now.

835
00:58:11,600 --> 00:58:15,300
Just hit me if you're going to. Let the other kids go.

836
00:58:15,300 --> 00:58:17,580
They have nothing to do with it.

837
00:58:19,930 --> 00:58:24,700
♪  The hibiscus flowers have blossomed  ♪

838
00:58:25,770 --> 00:58:29,930
♪  They blossomed so freaking flashingly  ♪

839
00:58:32,000 --> 00:58:37,420
I just want to step on the ground, but the petals keep falling.

840
00:58:37,420 --> 00:58:40,820
What can I do? I have no choice...

841
00:58:40,820 --> 00:58:43,920
but to step on all of them. Don't you think?

842
00:58:45,610 --> 00:58:47,190
Stomp on them.

843
00:58:51,290 --> 00:58:54,170
- We've met before, right? 
 - I don't want to see you!

844
00:58:56,330 --> 00:58:58,170
Get them now!

845
00:58:58,960 --> 00:59:00,560
Get them!

846
00:59:29,740 --> 00:59:32,320
- Are you okay? 
 - Of course.

847
00:59:33,490 --> 00:59:35,190
Shit!

848
00:59:42,120 --> 00:59:43,710
Young man.

849
00:59:43,710 --> 00:59:45,590
Young man!

850
00:59:45,590 --> 00:59:47,850
H-Hey, young man.

851
00:59:47,850 --> 00:59:50,690
Hey, young man. Are you okay?

852
00:59:51,450 --> 00:59:53,020
- Are you okay? 
 - I'm fine, I'm fine.

853
01:00:22,920 --> 01:00:24,310
Move it!

854
01:00:47,920 --> 01:00:50,690
 You get into an accident if you go to the rehearsal. 

855
01:00:50,690 --> 01:00:55,550
 Because of that accident, your life changes. 

856
01:00:55,550 --> 01:00:57,110
 Is this what he meant? 

857
01:00:57,110 --> 01:00:59,260
 I know your future 

858
01:00:59,260 --> 01:01:02,380
 and I found a way to change your life. 

859
01:01:03,690 --> 01:01:05,320
 That was... 

860
01:01:06,240 --> 01:01:07,410
 really true? 

861
01:01:07,410 --> 01:01:09,970
I need to be careful.

862
01:01:09,970 --> 01:01:12,290
But they always force me to.

863
01:01:13,390 --> 01:01:15,660
Hey!

864
01:01:21,210 --> 01:01:25,100
Don't touch Lee Chan, you sons of bitches!

865
01:01:34,010 --> 01:01:38,130
I said don't touch Lee Chan, you son of a bitch!

866
01:01:40,200 --> 01:01:42,910
There's police outside!

867
01:01:43,820 --> 01:01:45,610
Let's run!

868
01:01:51,560 --> 01:01:53,700
Lee Chan.

869
01:01:53,700 --> 01:01:56,160
Please wake up. Please?

870
01:01:56,160 --> 01:01:59,080
Open your eyes, please?

871
01:01:59,080 --> 01:02:01,090
Can you hear me?

872
01:02:01,090 --> 01:02:04,150
Answer me! Can you hear me?

873
01:02:05,360 --> 01:02:08,920
You're so loud. Be quiet.

874
01:02:08,920 --> 01:02:11,190
Can you hear my voice?

875
01:02:12,810 --> 01:02:14,820
Yes.

876
01:02:14,820 --> 01:02:16,680
I can hear everything.

877
01:02:28,910 --> 01:02:30,560
 I prevented it. 

878
