880
01:02:45,170 --> 01:02:53,610
♫  I'm alone on top of the clock's hand  ♫

881
01:02:53,610 --> 01:03:01,240
♫  All the days I've run, all that time  ♫

882
01:03:03,840 --> 01:03:08,780
   

883
01:03:08,780 --> 01:03:10,320
 There's something you don't know about. 

884
01:03:10,320 --> 01:03:13,610
 I hate being abandoned more than anything. 

885
01:03:13,610 --> 01:03:15,360
 I won't go easy on you today. 

886
01:03:15,360 --> 01:03:17,060
 You think only you have it? I have one, too. 

887
01:03:17,060 --> 01:03:20,300
 About the secret that I said I'd tell when it's time. I'll tell you everything now. 

888
01:03:20,300 --> 01:03:21,590
 Please choose me. 

889
01:03:21,590 --> 01:03:25,460
 It's love. You'll get very good lyrics later. 

890
01:03:25,460 --> 01:03:27,630
 No, the festival ended. 

891
01:03:27,630 --> 01:03:29,060
 Don't come to see me anymore. 

892
01:03:29,060 --> 01:03:30,770
 Can't you just leave me alone? 

893
01:03:30,770 --> 01:03:32,640
 We won't have to see each other again. 

894
01:03:32,640 --> 01:03:35,630
 You and I live in different worlds, anyway. 

895
01:03:35,630 --> 01:03:37,790
 It's been fun, Lee Chan. 

